October 2017 vs October 2018 📸
After teaming up with @stadionparkklinikken one year ago, healthier food choices along with being more active on a daily basis has been a big part of my life 🏋🏼‍♂️🧗🏼‍♂️🏃🏼‍♂️🙌🏼
Last fall I wanted to feel better, to have more energy in general and to be able to maintain a healthier weight - I just wanted to be a better version of me 💯🙋🏼‍♂️
And I’m proud to say that with genuine coaching by the #stadionparkklinikken staff and alot of hard work and effort I’m on the right path to reach my goal 🎯 #TransformationTuesday 🤗
Hopefully this post can motivate some of you guys who is in the same situation I was in - you can ALL do it! 💪🏼 💪🏼💪🏼
That being said I wish you all a good, active week 👏🏼😃😅 #PersonalTraining #Physiotherapy #Chiropractor #Weightloss #Performance #Motivation #Crossfit #Fit #Results #HealthyLifestyle #ActiveLifestyle #JustDoIt
